    <item>
      <title>原油期货进入超买区域后涨势减弱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-june-21</link>
      <description><![CDATA[原油期货进入超买区域后下跌，但由于美国库存减少和燃料需求上升的迹象，原油价格仍保持每周上涨的势头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-june-21</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 23:23:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
